data.description:
Are you ready to plant your feet on some country living? This stunning countryside home offers just about everything you need on 10 glorious acres. Property has a charming one-bedroom/one bath guest house with its very own comfy setting and parking area. Guest house is equipped with heating/ cooling with a kitchen including a stove and refrigerator, a living area. The guest house is approximate 512 sq. ft. The main house amenities include a 15x20 gym/sauna room, an 8x12 office/he/she shed building, 10x16 workshop, a 12x30 storage building, a 10x12 feed/supply building, and a 4x8 chicken coop. The office, workshop, and storage building all have available electricity. Let's not forget the Canter Power Systems GENERAC with its own propane tank. A new composition class 4 roof was installed in 2021. New Smart 3 Glass double-pane windows were installed in 2022 throughout the house. Property is also built for family and friends as well. Home has an firepit for evening gathering and an above pool with a deck for those hot summer days coming. Home location is in a low tax rate!! This home is a MUST SEE!!
***All DEMENSIONS AND MEASUREMENTS ARE APPROXIMATE** Buyer to verify.
